<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٨٦)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" مَا جزر عَنهُ الْبَحْر فكلوه "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٨٧)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" لَا تأذنوا لمن لَا يبْدَأ بِالسَّلَامِ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٨٨)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" كَانَ النَّبِي - صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّم َ - لَا يَأْذَن لمن لَا يبْدَأ بِالسَّلَامِ "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٨٩)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" لكل دَاء دَوَاء "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>